OL,4,Chospice which cared for both his
OL,5,Cpartners
OL,7,FHe said: "Nicky was big into her
OL,8,Frunning and she used to run three
OL,9,Ftimes a week, up to 25 miles a week,
OL,10,Fand we used to do some half marathons
OL,11,Fand run together.
OL,13,F"Nicky would glide as a runner,
OL,14,Fwhereas although I come from a
OL,15,Fsporting background, I would sometimes
OL,16,Flook a bit awkward when I ran, and
OL,17,FNicky would always jokingly tell me,
OL,18,F'look at your face, why don't you run
OL,19,Fwith a smile. It will be easier if you
OL,20,Frun with a smile'."
